Filter holder lor a coffee machine
Filter holder for a coffee machine comprising a
main body (1) formed of an upper part (1.1) and a lower
part (1.2), a filter-ejector (5) that can axially slide in said
upper part (1.1), a first cam (4) that is located below the
filter-ejector (5) and is adapted to engage and raise the
latter upon a first relative rotation between both, in order
to reduce the volume ofthe coffee powderto be brewed,
and a second cam (3) that is fixed to the first cam (4) and
is adapted to engage and further raise the filter-ejector
(5) upon a second relative rotation between both, in order
to eject the coffee grounds after a coffee has been
brewed. The filter-ejector (5) is keyed to said lower part
(1.2), so that both the first and second cam can rotate
